				ok.  to all those people who say &quot;i'll leave it up to you to discover this....blah blah..&quot; i think you are being lame.  if you are not gonna post spoilers, don't post on spoiler threads.<BR>
<BR>
second.  the third scale is gotten from temple of solusek ro.  the high elf drops it, but you can also do a quest for him.  he needs tektite or some stone by the simular name that comes off a gargoyle in overthere by the same name.  the gargoyle is hard to kill and very magic resistant.  <BR>
<BR>
however, an evil char can get tektite from him by giving him to carnelians.  after you get it, go to your nearest jewlery store, and purchase 1 peridot.  give the tektite and peridot to Xyfl (the high elf in temple of solusek ro) and he will give you his scale.<BR>
<BR>
the other two scales are obtained from the two wurms in burning wood, as the original poster already stated, and are pretty straightforward.<BR>
<BR>
the biggest problem of the quest tho, for me at least, is finding Squire Fuzzmin or whatever his name is now :(  i have the 3 scales and i just need to find him, but the lil bastard is impossible to find, hehe<BR>
<BR>
btw, the Wurmslayer is 25 40 piercing (1hnd, primary only) 5 ac, 5 str, 5 vs magic RANGE 20 (if you are dumb enuf to throw it, dont put it in range, hehe) and 15 weight.<BR>
<BR>
good luck!
